the idea myself.  More likely, someone who had read Hoffer made the observa=
tion to me and I was ready to hear it.  The complaint about "the 1%" from 1=
0-20 years ago came from the 5-20% - or their children, who feared they wer=
e not going to make it that far and needed to declare the system rigged and=
 unfair. </span></p><div role=3D"button" class=3D"show-all-toggle"><div cla=
